WEBVTT

00:03.774 --> 00:07.111
THEY CALLED ME MAYDAY

00:11.449 --> 00:14.243
- Morning, Norm.
- Morning, Sam.

00:15.661 --> 00:18.456
- Coffee's on.
- Great. Any calls?

00:20.583 --> 00:24.879
- Vera called this morning.
- You guys gonna patch it up?

00:25.046 --> 00:28.549
No. She just wanted to reach out
and nag someone.

00:35.139 --> 00:37.600
Come on. Admit it, Norm. You miss her.

00:38.893 --> 00:41.687
Yeah. Yeah, I do miss her.

00:41.854 --> 00:46.108
There's only one thing that keeps me
from taking her back right now.

00:46.275 --> 00:49.403
- She kicked you out on your butt.
- Right.

00:50.613 --> 00:53.949
- I appreciate you letting me crash here.
- Don't mention it.

00:54.116 --> 00:57.244
When I get back on my feet,
I'll pay you some kind of rent.

00:57.411 --> 01:01.457
- That's not necessary.
- I have my pride to consider.

01:01.624 --> 01:05.878
All right. Pay me a dollar a month.

01:06.962 --> 01:09.006
For what?

01:10.675 --> 01:14.595
- How about 50 cents?
- Fine. No cleaning deposit.

01:16.305 --> 01:18.432
- We're low on cream.
- I'll get on it.

01:18.599 --> 01:20.893
No rush.

